result.name: foreign-office-consular-data
result.notes:
This data is now published by The Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office.  
These data gives information about the Foreign Office Consular data on Consular services provided to British nationals worldwide this includes numbers of incidents handled by UK consulates overseas, including hospitalisations, deaths, detentions, with geographical location.  FCO merged with the Department for International Development on 1 September 2020. This data continues to be published on the Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Offices publication page.
